  dialogue:
  - Why are you showing me a dead bird, sir?
  - Tis 'n albatross, lad.
  - "Tis a foul omen te find 'em like this.\r"
  - "Do you actually believe that?\r"
  - "'t don't matter if ye believe or not,\r"
  - "ye can only hope fer the Sea's mercy.\r"
  - "...\r"
  - "Ye head inside now, lad. I'll deal with the body.\r"
